caption.title: Enrichment analysis of responsive genes and transcripts using GO terms for Wenzhou (WZ) versus Haikou (HK).
caption.p: The node size is proportional to the number of targets in the GO category. Node color represents enriched significance; a deeper color represents a higher significance [a1, a2, and a3: total (topGO_BP, topGO_CC, and topGO_MF); b1, b2, and b3: down-regulated (topGO_BP, topGO_CC, and topGO_MF); c1, c2, and c3: up-regulated (topGO_BP, topGO_CC, and topGO_MF)].
